Date: Wed, 14 Feb 2018 21:23:26 +0200
Subject: drm/i915: Change the COLOR_ENCODING prop default value to BT.709
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 23b280890a140b0cf1e8f61c252936c2fb77f718
Patch-mainline: v4.17-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

Bring us forward from the stone age and switch our default YCbCr->RGB
conversion matrix to BT.709 from BT.601. I would expect most matrial
to be BT.709 these days.

